<br>
Now on to the more serious side of my statement.<br>
<br>
Having lived and trained and gathered intelligence and in some cases fought against the peoples who are most likely responsible for this reprehensible act. <br>
<br>
There is only way to fight back against such extremists, and thats to cause such losses that Fear will keep them from ever, even in the shadow of thier minds from planning or trying to carry out such an attack against anyone in the civilized world.<br>
 <br>
Using Terror as a weapon against those while distasteful is in this case the only effective way to cease the enemies will to fight and attack innocent civilians and unfortunately we'll have to learn how to wage such a war as the United States has always sought to aid those around us including those we've conquered.(Germany, Italy and Japan among others.)<br>
