<br>
To wage war against those who serve the Jihad we must launch our own equivelant to Jihad and show the enemy our grim resolve to cause them such loss as to pacify them through fear of extinction.<br>
<br>
I do not paint with a broad brush the many millions of peaceful Muslims who shouldn't feel our wrath. I do target those who support Muslim terror groups, such groups as The Base(Bin Ladens bunch) Hammas, the militant arm of the PLO, Islamic Jihad many others and I would dare to include the American Nazi party and the Klu Klux Klan as groups who should also be put out of business and many organizations the world over. <br>
