This is an opportunity to extinguish terror groups the world over lets hope the governments of the world sieze upon this opportunity to clean the worlds proverbial house out.<br>
<br>
Now whether people choose to brand me a racist or not is not something I care about. I tell it straight as someone who has seen the real data of what the reality of the situation is.<br>
<br>
